<br>
With the addition of Beastlords and the fact that My Mage is only 11 now, I have gotten into many Pet groups in Everfrost.  Was in a group with 4 beastlords and me.  We rocked.  I did figure out that we have a huge advantage when our Pet gets killed while grouped.  We can just summon up a new one and send it into battle while the ones they summon start out green.<br>
